Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.67,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,42
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.57,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,43
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.24,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.19,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,44
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.98,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 不要打了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.89,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再管我了 別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:54.95,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.98,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,難得和你相處融洽起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:02.67,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,我可受不了再次絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.13,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,你..在這狀態 在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.53,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.43,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:14.29,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能不管你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.76,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.26,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,50
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.26,gosick,,0000,0000,0000,,51
